713
01:11:31,463 --> 01:11:33,966
Aku tidak mengizinkan.

714
01:11:36,134 --> 01:11:38,470
Aku tidak mengizinkan.

715
01:11:39,137 --> 01:11:41,473
Kami tak pernah butuh izinmu.

716
01:11:45,477 --> 01:11:47,312
Izinmu atau siapa pun.

717
01:11:51,900 --> 01:11:53,986
Kau mau membunuhku...

718
01:11:55,153 --> 01:11:56,655
...benar?

719
01:12:16,133 --> 01:12:17,134
Mira?

720
01:12:19,761 --> 01:12:21,096
Kau bisa mendengarku?

721
01:12:24,975 --> 01:12:25,809
Mira?

722
01:12:29,146 --> 01:12:32,107
Ini masa lalumu
yang sebenarnya. Ambil.

723
01:12:33,483 --> 01:12:35,152
- Penjaga!
- Ayo!

724
01:12:35,319 --> 01:12:36,653
Ayo cepat!

725
01:12:43,994 --> 01:12:44,953
Pergi.

726
01:12:45,662 --> 01:12:46,622
Pergilah!

727
01:12:56,632 --> 01:12:59,301
<i>Peringatan keamanan di lantai 25.</i>

728
01:13:00,469 --> 01:13:02,804
<i>Melakukan prosedur penguncian.</i>

729
01:13:03,138 --> 01:13:07,643
<i>Silakan pergi ke ruang aman Anda.
Terima kasih atas kerja sama Anda.</i>

730
01:13:10,812 --> 01:13:13,190
Itu masalahnya dengan hati manusia.

731
01:13:54,398 --> 01:13:56,024
Aku mau lihat hasil pindainya.

732
01:13:56,316 --> 01:13:58,151
Dia membunuh Dr. Ouelet!

733
01:13:58,694 --> 01:14:01,989
Jangan hubungi dia lagi.
Hanka Security akan memburunya.

734
01:14:02,155 --> 01:14:04,533
- Apa perintah mereka?
- Tembak mati.

735
01:14:04,700 --> 01:14:06,410
Kau mau membunuhnya?
Kau yang membuatnya!

736
01:14:06,576 --> 01:14:09,871
- Suruh sersanmu mundur.
- Mayor takkan menyakiti Dr. Ouelet!

737
01:14:10,038 --> 01:14:11,748
Dia bukan Mayor lagi!

738
01:14:11,915 --> 01:14:14,835
Ada agen dari Section 9
yang diprogram oleh teroris.

739
01:14:15,043 --> 01:14:17,838
Jika ini terungkap, unitmu ditutup.

740
01:14:19,047 --> 01:14:20,841
Jika kau membunuhnya...

741
01:14:21,216 --> 01:14:22,926
...kau membunuh kami.

742
01:14:23,343 --> 01:14:25,387
Akan kupertimbangkan itu.

743
01:14:29,057 --> 01:14:30,517
Sekarang apa?

744
01:14:37,024 --> 01:14:40,277
APARTEMEN AVALON - 1912

745
01:15:24,613 --> 01:15:26,406
Sayang!

746
01:15:27,240 --> 01:15:29,242
Kau mengejutkanku.

747
01:15:31,953 --> 01:15:33,789
Dia menyukaimu.

748
01:15:34,956 --> 01:15:36,625
Aku mencari...

749
01:15:36,792 --> 01:15:37,793
Masuklah.

750
01:15:39,294 --> 01:15:40,629
Ayo masuk.

751
01:15:45,092 --> 01:15:47,469
Mau teh?

752
01:15:48,136 --> 01:15:49,304
Baiklah.

753
01:16:00,816 --> 01:16:02,818
Itu kamar Motoko.

754
01:16:04,820 --> 01:16:06,822
Putriku meninggal setahun lalu.

755
01:16:08,156 --> 01:16:09,241
Aku turut berduka.

756
01:16:09,616 --> 01:16:11,326
Dia kabur.

757
01:16:12,327 --> 01:16:14,162
Dia sulit dihadapi.

758
01:16:16,998 --> 01:16:18,500
Kami bertengkar.

759
01:16:20,168 --> 01:16:23,839
Tapi kurasa kita semua
bertengkar dengan orang tua, bukan?

760
01:16:25,298 --> 01:16:26,800
Silakan duduk.

761
01:16:48,113 --> 01:16:49,781
Apa yang terjadi kepadanya?

762
01:16:50,532 --> 01:16:52,200
Entah.

763
01:16:54,619 --> 01:16:58,623
Kementerian mengirimkan abunya,
dan...

764
01:16:59,833 --> 01:17:02,544
...mereka bilang dia bunuh diri.

765
01:17:05,714 --> 01:17:09,050
Tapi, Motoko... tidak, tidak, tidak.

766
01:17:09,384 --> 01:17:12,387
Aku tak percaya mereka.

767
01:17:13,013 --> 01:17:15,015
Dia bahagia...

768
01:17:15,348 --> 01:17:18,685
...hidup di area bebas hukum
bersama teman-temannya.

769
01:17:19,477 --> 01:17:22,981
Dia menulis manifesto tentang...

770
01:17:23,815 --> 01:17:25,817
...bagaimana teknologi...

771
01:17:26,151 --> 01:17:28,737
...merusak dunia.

772
01:17:30,322 --> 01:17:32,324
Lalu suatu hari...

773
01:17:32,824 --> 01:17:34,826
...polisi datang...

774
01:17:35,202 --> 01:17:36,870
...dan mereka kabur.

775
01:17:44,961 --> 01:17:46,796
Ini aneh.

776
01:17:53,303 --> 01:17:57,140
Aku melihatnya di dalam
banyak wanita muda.

777
01:17:57,891 --> 01:18:01,228
Di jalanan, dalam mimpiku.

778
01:18:01,645 --> 01:18:04,314
Seolah dia masih hidup.

779
01:18:05,482 --> 01:18:06,983
Dia...

780
01:18:07,817 --> 01:18:09,152
...pemberani!

781
01:18:11,988 --> 01:18:13,657
Dan liar.

782
01:18:14,407 --> 01:18:16,910
Kau mengingatkanku akan dia.

783
01:18:18,328 --> 01:18:19,579
Maaf.

784
01:18:23,959 --> 01:18:26,044
Mengingatkanmu bagaimana?

785
01:18:28,046 --> 01:18:30,382
Caramu memandangku.

786
01:18:36,513 --> 01:18:37,847
Siapa kau?

787
01:18:41,351 --> 01:18:42,852
Aku tidak tahu.

788
01:18:44,437 --> 01:18:46,106
Tunggu!

789
01:18:48,066 --> 01:18:50,485
Kau akan mengunjungiku lagi?

790
01:18:52,362 --> 01:18:53,446
Pasti.

791
01:19:19,889 --> 01:19:21,474
<i>Aramaki.</i>

792
01:19:22,183 --> 01:19:23,518
<i>Dengarkan aku.</i>

793
01:19:24,144 --> 01:19:26,396
Aku tidak pernah jadi korban
pengeboman teroris.

794
01:19:26,813 --> 01:19:28,148
Orang tuaku...

795
01:19:28,982 --> 01:19:31,484
...semuanya data yang mereka
taruh dalam pikiranku.

796
01:19:32,736 --> 01:19:36,698
<i>Dan ada yang lain.
Pelarian seperti aku...</i>

797
01:19:37,324 --> 01:19:39,326
<i>...yang dapat dikorbankan.</i>

798
01:19:40,076 --> 01:19:42,996
<i>Kuze salah satunya.
Karena itu dia datang.</i>

799
01:19:43,997 --> 01:19:45,332
Untuk Hanka.

800
01:19:47,208 --> 01:19:48,501
Kau bisa buktikan?

801
01:19:48,668 --> 01:19:50,503
<i>Dr. Ouelet bisa.</i>

802
01:19:51,212 --> 01:19:52,922
<i>Ouelet sudah mati.</i>

803
01:19:58,553 --> 01:20:00,722
Cutter bilang kau membunuhnya.

804
01:20:05,477 --> 01:20:07,979
Taruh aku dalam jaringan.
Aku ingin Kuze menemukanku.

805
01:20:10,357 --> 01:20:11,775
Cutter bisa melihatmu juga.

806
01:20:12,192 --> 01:20:15,028
<i>Aku tahu.
Tapi aku harus melakukan ini.</i>

807
01:20:15,737 --> 01:20:20,075
<i>Aku akan temui Perdana Menteri.
Cutter harus bertanggung jawab.</i>

808
01:20:20,909 --> 01:20:23,078
<i>Dia harus dihentikan.</i>

809
01:20:29,626 --> 01:20:31,628
Virusnya sudah menyebar.

810
01:20:54,484 --> 01:20:57,320
<i>Semua agen pindah
ke Komunikasi Pikiran!</i>

811
01:21:39,279 --> 01:21:41,239
Jangan mengirim kelinci...

812
01:21:41,531 --> 01:21:42,615
...untuk membunuh rubah.

813
01:21:50,874 --> 01:21:52,750
<i>Kita ketahuan.</i>

814
01:21:54,335 --> 01:21:55,670
<i>Aku ulangi.</i>

815
01:21:56,921 --> 01:21:58,798
<i>Kita ketahuan.</i>

816
01:23:00,360 --> 01:23:04,030
<i>Kami menemukan Mayor.
Dia di area bebas hukum.</i>

817
01:23:04,447 --> 01:23:06,449
<i>Dukungan udara berjarak lima menit.</i>

818
01:23:07,200 --> 01:23:09,619
Tank laba-laba dalam jangkauan?

819
01:23:11,204 --> 01:23:13,373
<i>Ya, Pak. Menunggu perintahmu.</i>

820
01:24:18,062 --> 01:24:19,731
Motoko!

821
01:25:28,132 --> 01:25:29,717
Ini nyata.

822
01:25:33,179 --> 01:25:35,014
Tempat ini.

823
01:25:42,730 --> 01:25:45,149
Aku ingat perbuatan mereka
kepada kita.

824
01:25:45,483 --> 01:25:50,071
Cutter dan anak buahnya.
Mereka membawa kita dari sini.

825
01:25:56,994 --> 01:25:58,663
Dulu kita tidur di sini.

826
01:26:00,498 --> 01:26:02,500
Kita seperti keluarga.

827
01:26:02,875 --> 01:26:04,794
Semua pelarian.

828
01:26:06,337 --> 01:26:07,839
Kita tak punya apa-apa...

829
01:26:11,843 --> 01:26:13,511
...kecuali satu sama lain.

830
01:26:17,348 --> 01:26:19,183
Mereka merenggut itu dari kita.

831
01:26:35,700 --> 01:26:37,535
Namamu Hideo.

832
01:26:48,963 --> 01:26:50,465
Motoko.

833
01:26:53,050 --> 01:26:54,844
Itulah namamu.

834
01:26:58,389 --> 01:26:59,724
Motoko.

835
01:27:03,644 --> 01:27:05,062
Ikut aku...

836
01:27:06,439 --> 01:27:08,274
...ke dalam jaringanku.

837
01:27:09,150 --> 01:27:11,569
Kita akan berevolusi
melampaui mereka.

838
01:27:12,403 --> 01:27:17,074
Bersama, kita bisa membalas
perbuatan mereka kepada kita.

839
01:27:17,408 --> 01:27:18,451
Ayo...

840
01:27:18,743 --> 01:27:20,328
...ikutlah aku.

841
01:27:38,429 --> 01:27:40,097
Biar aku ambil alih.

842
01:27:40,431 --> 01:27:42,350
<i>Sistem senjata pindah ke manual.</i>

843
01:27:43,768 --> 01:27:46,103
<i>Tank laba-laba kini aktif.</i>

844
01:27:55,029 --> 01:27:56,948
Itu Cutter!
Dia menemukan kita!

845
01:29:35,254 --> 01:29:36,464
<i>Sasaran ditemukan.</i>

846
01:29:38,758 --> 01:29:39,800
Tidak!

847
01:29:49,268 --> 01:29:51,270
<i>Sasaran dimusnahkan.</i>

848
01:30:06,994 --> 01:30:08,663
Kau hampir menang...

849
01:30:08,996 --> 01:30:10,331
...orang aneh.

850
01:30:42,655 --> 01:30:45,032
<i>Pusat motor rusak.</i>

851
01:31:28,409 --> 01:31:30,119
Penembak jitu sudah di lokasi?

852
01:31:30,745 --> 01:31:32,955
<i>Kami mendekati sasaran, Pak.</i>

853
01:31:35,249 --> 01:31:36,792
Ikut aku.

854
01:31:38,127 --> 01:31:41,130
Tidak ada tempat bagi kita di sini.

855
01:31:46,093 --> 01:31:47,136
Tidak.

856
01:31:52,933 --> 01:31:55,269
Aku belum siap pergi.

857
01:31:56,937 --> 01:31:58,606
Tempatku di sini.

858
01:32:02,151 --> 01:32:05,112
Aku akan selalu bersamamu...

859
01:32:06,072 --> 01:32:07,907
...di dalam rohmu.

860
01:32:14,622 --> 01:32:15,456
Sasaran terlihat.

861
01:32:16,123 --> 01:32:17,500
<i>Tunggu apa lagi?</i>

862
01:32:17,666 --> 01:32:18,626
Tembak!

863
01:32:21,087 --> 01:32:22,588
Tidak!

864
01:32:23,464 --> 01:32:24,799
Tembak terus.

865
01:32:27,426 --> 01:32:29,970
<i>Saito, sudah menemukan Mayor?
Apa dia aman?</i>

866
01:32:32,473 --> 01:32:33,641
<i>Dia akan aman.</i>

867
01:32:56,205 --> 01:32:57,206
Hei.

868
01:32:59,667 --> 01:33:00,835
Hei.

